title: Townhouse 2 Bedrooms 2.5 Bathrooms in Miami Lakes
posting_body: ['Feast your eyes and fall in love with this beautiful waterfront townhome in Miami Lakes!', 'This wonderful property comes tastefully furnished with amazing finishes throughout.', 'Formal dining, lovely kitchen with stainless steel appliances, grand open, airy living room over looking the patio where can sit and relax under the pergola', 'and then you have lounge chairs for you to soak up the sun and enjoy the lake view!', 'Upstairs you have two roomy bedrooms each with their own private bathroom.', 'The master suite offers amazing natural light through balcony doors where you can again, enjoy the lake view from sunrise to sundown!', 'Centrally located near amazing restaurants, Starbucks, shops and plenty to do!', "Don't miss out on this grand opportunity!", 'Fred Ardjmand Licensed Real Estate Associate', 'show contact info', '.', 'Courtesy of  Stratwell, LLC']
